## Testing Checklist

Before submitting changes to this module, verify:

1. `npx tsc --noEmit` passes in both `backend/crm-backend` and `frontend/crm-frontend`
2. `npx jest --passWithNoTests` passes in `backend/crm-backend` (199+ tests)
3. After deployment, run `npx prisma migrate deploy` on Railway if schema changed
4. Test with at least one channel (WhatsApp or Telegram) to verify:
   - New messages appear in inbox
   - Customer name displays correctly (not raw ID)
   - Notification sound plays
   - Operator can join and reply
   - Manager sees all conversations
